title: event.availableTo
description:
The last date & time that the [event](./event.json) is allowed to be visible on publication channels.

Added automatically by UiTdatabank based on either the [startDate](./event-startDate.json) or [endDate](./event-endDate.json) depending on the [event type](./event-terms.json).

Formatted as an ISO-8601 datetime. For example `2021-05-17T22:00:00+00:00`.
